This paper is about image labeling using deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the architecture and training of the network, which are topics that fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of recursive iterations and statistical dependencies in label space suggests that the paper may also be relevant to neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses the application of the proposed method to connectomic reconstruction, which is a topic that falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
